Hey, thanks for previously downloading one of my mods. I've now released my first proper mod thats actually worth downloading!

---- Cycle ----

Cycle adds menstruation and woohoo risk as problems your sims must deal with. Trying for babies is no longer so easy, and having a night of ecstasy with your partner is no longer so safe. Use caution to avoid unwanted rug rats or carefully track your sim's fertility in order start a family.

If your seeing this message its probably because recently downloaded my latest mod: Cycle.

Except you didn't.

Contrary to my instructions you only downloaded Cycle's required toolkit. I thought I said you needed to download both, but I guess I wasn't clear enough for about 40% of you.
Come back and download the actual mod you numbskull. :)
